Biography

Jim Carrey is a Canadian-American actor, comedian and artist, known for his energetic slapstick performance. Though he is best known for his comedic roles, he has also shown his skill in more dramatic performances.[1]

James Eugene Carrey was born 17 January 1962 in Newmarket, Ontario. He is the son of Percy Carrey and Kathleen Oram.

Jim married Melissa Womer in 1987. They were divorced in 1995. Jim married Lauren Holly in 1996. They were divorced in 1997. Jim had a serious relationship with Jenny McCarthy from 2005 to 2010.

Jim is still living.
